column3:
“Not much of an indica smoker but as a hybrid this is the best of both worlds.  The earthy notes on this strain are awesome this has to be one of my favorite indica hybrid strains due to the potency level of high and how enjoyable it is to smoke. For 2 months I have had this strain and it hasn't worn on me yet or lost its appeal definitely coming back for more
Perfecto!!!'
@leafybuddah”
